{"tid":1627183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌晒黃大仙grp啲人","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:52.000Z","uid":201091,"like":443,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"89027a782de2bca3fa10b7ca84499339e975364a","tid":1627183,"uid":201091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"我屌晒你地老母<br />\n一早講好咗5點出黎<br />\n點撚知出到黎<br />\n得個十條友都冇<br />\n咁都算撚數啦<br />\n之後又話8點<br />\n等撚到8點<br />\n都仲係得個三十幾四十個<br />\n咁唯有自己搞啦<br />\n由黃大仙搞撚到樂富<br />\n係樂富巴士總站有人被人拉<br />\n到我地走晒<br />\n班仆街先話而家出<br />\n咁我就屌佢哋老母啦<br />\n點知仲話攰要休息<br />\n我唔撚攰既？<br />\n一句攰大撚晒<br />\n攰得過前線？<br />\n攰得過俾人拉嗰啲手足？<br />\n最後我講返句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你地老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"7dc59b29efc7035b7c58479dcf1b9598aef96a06","tid":1627183,"uid":201091,"like":18,"dislike":9,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"你哋咁鍾意休息<br />\n休多幾日先啦"},{"pid":"6589736ff33d2257e114d98c98c34e104c2f3884","tid":1627183,"uid":216070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"和理非街坊look都唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721d047df14016622755756f9ca92bcd5b7ef5da","tid":1627183,"uid":49336,"like":63,"dislike":5,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"如果啲人講完出但係唔出就仆街啫<br />\n而家唔想出咪唔出囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又屌手足"},{"pid":"f9ad791433df883928d04ddbbe86043d8e788e90","tid":1627183,"uid":201091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6589736ff33d2257e114d98c98c34e104c2f3884","tid":1627183,"uid":216070,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"和理非街坊look都唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"攰吖嘛"},{"pid":"f96ef3811c603d284d87cdf9a354a141eacbda31","tid":1627183,"uid":201091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc